data.description: GULF ACCESS POOL HOME W/add'l Garage & outdoor KITCHEN!  Welcome to your dream home in Cape Coral! This stunning single-family home offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. This triple lot pool home comes with 3 beds/3 baths and 2 garages, there is ample space for your family to spread out and enjoy.  The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite counters, SS appliances, and a spacious layout that is perfect for entertaining. Step outside and be prepared to be amazed by the outdoor oasis that awaits you.  Roof & A/C (2) 2021.   This pool is perfect for those hot summer days, and the outdoor kitchen is ideal for hosting unforgettable gatherings with friends and family. With a composite boat lift and dock, you have direct Gulf access right from your backyard, making it a boater's paradise. Spend your weekends exploring the beautiful waterways and discovering hidden gems along the coast. This home truly has it all. Located in the desirable Yacht Club area, you will enjoy the tranquility of waterfront living while still being just a short drive away from shopping, dining, and entertainment options.  Assumable VA loan 3, subject to qualifications.
